  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1245370/extras/e10840ef2e6f2a072500603e223e154c.poster.avif?t=1698174890\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1245370/extras/e10840ef2e6f2a072500603e223e154c.webm?t=1698174890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1245370/extras/e10840ef2e6f2a072500603e223e154c.mp4?t=1698174890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Craft, attack, repeat.</strong><br>Puzzle Forge Dungeon is a turn-based crawler from the original series of <i>Puzzle Forge</i>. Create weapons with a match-3 system on your board and throw them to the enemies. Each battle is unique and requires you to use resources and skills cleverly.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1245370/extras/7f02a392a61f5a3f539d83b3cd9ae7a3.poster.avif?t=1698174890\" width=616 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1245370/extras/7f02a392a61f5a3f539d83b3cd9ae7a3.webm?t=1698174890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1245370/extras/7f02a392a61f5a3f539d83b3cd9ae7a3.mp4?t=1698174890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Help dwarves to reconquer their city</strong><br>Anvilars’ forges turned off! The last inhabitants ask every blacksmith available to help restore the city and repair the Heart of Anvilar.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Discover gameplay mechanics while exploring the city.<br></li><li>Cleaning a district will unlock services and/or heroes.<br></li><li>Complete all districts open a new infinite, procedurally generated game mode.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1245370/extras/e0162c73c9bafc998c6ce0b5b782d219.avif?t=1698174890\" width=616 height=252 /></span><br><strong>Manage a team of heroes</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Recruit, heal and upgrade your heroes.<br></li><li>Discover heroes stories during specific enemy encounters.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1245370/extras/19011dd3132e58d4a20b5e00a8e474f6.avif?t=1698174890\" width=616 height=180 /></span><br><strong>A parodic bestiary</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>50 different enemies.<br></li><li>Unique bosses.<br></li><li>Procedural enemy group generation.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1245370/extras/e10840ef2e6f2a072500603e223e154c.poster.avif?t=1698174890\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1245370/extras/e10840ef2e6f2a072500603e223e154c.webm?t=1698174890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1245370/extras/e10840ef2e6f2a072500603e223e154c.mp4?t=1698174890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Craft, attack, repeat.</strong><br>Puzzle Forge Dungeon is a turn-based crawler from the original series of <i>Puzzle Forge</i>. Create weapons with a match-3 system on your board and throw them to the enemies. Each battle is unique and requires you to use resources and skills cleverly.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1245370/extras/7f02a392a61f5a3f539d83b3cd9ae7a3.poster.avif?t=1698174890\" width=616 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1245370/extras/7f02a392a61f5a3f539d83b3cd9ae7a3.webm?t=1698174890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1245370/extras/7f02a392a61f5a3f539d83b3cd9ae7a3.mp4?t=1698174890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Help dwarves to reconquer their city</strong><br>Anvilars’ forges turned off! The last inhabitants ask every blacksmith available to help restore the city and repair the Heart of Anvilar.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Discover gameplay mechanics while exploring the city.<br></li><li>Cleaning a district will unlock services and/or heroes.<br></li><li>Complete all districts open a new infinite, procedurally generated game mode.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1245370/extras/e0162c73c9bafc998c6ce0b5b782d219.avif?t=1698174890\" width=616 height=252 /></span><br><strong>Manage a team of heroes</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Recruit, heal and upgrade your heroes.<br></li><li>Discover heroes stories during specific enemy encounters.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1245370/extras/19011dd3132e58d4a20b5e00a8e474f6.avif?t=1698174890\" width=616 height=180 /></span><br><strong>A parodic bestiary</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>50 different enemies.<br></li><li>Unique bosses.<br></li><li>Procedural enemy group generation.</li></ul>",
